---
import PublicLayout from '../layouts/PublicLayout.astro'
---
<PublicLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Upstate Web Co. collects, uses, and protects your data.">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: March 24, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Upstate Web Co. is a web design studio based in Greenville, South Carolina. This policy covers data collected through our website at upstate-web.com.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What Data We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Contact Form</h3>
        <p>When you submit our contact form, we collect your name, email address, business name (optional), and message. This data is sent to our inbox via Resend (our email provider) and is not stored in a database.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Email Signups</h3>
        <p>If you subscribe to updates, we collect your email address. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link in every email.</p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">Analytics</h3>
        <p>We use Cloudflare Analytics, which is cookieless and privacy-preserving. It collects no personal data and does not track individual users.</p>
        <p>If you accept cookies, we may use Meta Pixel and Google Ads for conversion tracking. These are only loaded after you consent.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our site uses one first-party cookie:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>uwc_consent</strong> — Records your cookie preference (accepted/rejected). Expires after 1 year.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">Third-party tracking cookies (Meta Pixel, Google Ads) are only set if you click "Accept" on the cookie banner. Cloudflare Analytics does not use cookies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">How We Use Your Data</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Contact form data: to respond to your inquiry</li>
          <li>Email signups: to send occasional updates about web design tips and services</li>
          <li>Analytics: to understand site traffic and improve our content</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We do not sell your data. We do not share it with third parties except the service providers listed below.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Service Providers</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> (hosting, analytics, DNS) — USA</li>
          <li><strong>Resend</strong> (email delivery) — USA</li>
          <li><strong>Anthropic</strong> (AI-assisted content drafting, admin only) — USA</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">All providers maintain appropriate data protection measures. For EU residents, transfers are covered by Standard Contractual Clauses.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Contact form submissions: retained in Resend for 30 days</li>
          <li>Email subscriptions: retained until you unsubscribe</li>
          <li>Analytics data: aggregated, no personal data retained</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for marketing emails at any time</li>
          <li>Decline cookies via the cookie banner</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">To exercise these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@upstate-web.com" class="text-[#B85C38] underline">hello@upstate-web.com</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">AI-Generated Content</h2>
        <p>Some of our social media content is drafted with the assistance of AI tools. All AI-generated content is reviewed and approved by a human before publishing.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top reflects the most recent changes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about this policy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@upstate-web.com" class="text-[#B85C38] underline">hello@upstate-web.com</a> or use our <a href="/contact" class="text-[#B85C38] underline">contact form</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</PublicLayout>
